        {
            "title": "Extra Info",
            "level": 1,
            "blocks":
            [
                {
                    "paragraph": "- LP is a resource, don't be afraid to take some hits, you have cards to recover so it is important to administrate your resources wisely."
                },   
                {
                    "paragraph": "- Cards like Burning Land are a double edge sword, don't play them immediately unless you are sure you can control the board and avoid taking hits, otherwise you will put yourself in disadvantage."
                },
                {
                    "paragraph": "- Temple of the Mind's Eye can be used for offense and defense, since all the battle damage gets reduced/increased to 1000."
                },
                {
                    "paragraph": "- Don't be afraid to force your opponent's backrow, cards like Inaba White Rabbit return to the hand at the end of the turn."
                }    
            ]
        }
